{
  "stem": "22652.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, with underwear and funny, cute little hat, and dress, and outfit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was overjoyed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So that was a surprise.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I also need to mention that when I got to meet Deniz 50 years later and I was on her list, there were 150 children on that list that she--",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She, she-- Deniz was the woman responsible for saving my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was the head of the French Underground, who was in charge of rescuing Jewish children, as well as countless thousands of refugees.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, on that list that I found myself in, there were 150 Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said that that list of 150 Jewish children, they were asking people for toys for, for us at the time of Christmas.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In those days, everybody celebrated Christmas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all of us, 150 children, got to receive a, a special Christmas toy on that day, in those dark moments.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, we never knew where the money was coming from that people would donate, and some of the money came from London.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During this time that you were in this convent, do you ever remember Germans coming to look at it?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Do you ever remember moments of danger where you might--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were told-- from what-- the way the nuns talked-- and we were told that we were in a very strat-- strategic, I don't know how you pronounce the word--",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--strategic position, because nearby was the headquarter of the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other side nearby was the headquarter of the French resistance, the Underground.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, as the liberation came near, we had the Americans drop-- and Allies dropping bombs all over us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it got to be-- incidentally, the nuns would called the Allies that we-- and the resistance as the terrorists.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
